snippet.title: PAC-MAN Party - Wii - E3 Trailer
snippet.description:
For more information visit: http://www.namcobandaigames.eu

Be some of the first to see this 'Never-Before-Seen' piece of E3 footage of PAC-MAN Party. This new edition of PAC-MAN, celebrating his 30 years of success,  has over 45 interactive fun mini-games  hosted by the Waka Waka king!
